name: Hut by the river on a winter night
description: Hut by the river on a winter night is a painting of a winter landscape with snow and a hut by a river in a winter night. The painting is in midnight blue, clouds can be seen. In front of a row of trees is a hut with a snow-white roof. The building is hidden by plants. A light is burning. The scene merges into a river in which the light of the night is reflected. The yellow moon or the sun.
